out a terms of reference until the new one was approved on February 2.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The new terms of reference provide more than just reference to the Senior Dean&rsquo;s powers. It lays down the rules for the Committee including its membership, meetings and quorum, and duties.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>", "Thumb_nail": "http://universitytimes.ie/wp-content/uploads/2013/utlogo.jpg", "ID": "18149", "Heading": "Capitation Committee settles on Senior Dean&#8217;s power"}